OL,3,CArrest in connection with kidnap of
OL,4,Cman, 87, who was dumped 15 miles away
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of kidnapping an 87-year-old
OL,8,Fwho was allegedly dragged into a car,
OL,9,Fblindfolded and thrown out in a
OL,10,Fdifferent county.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,13,Fthe man was reportedly walking home at
OL,14,F9pm on 15 September in the Lee Street
OL,15,Farea of Oldham when he was forced into
OL,16,Fa black car, while demands were made
OL,17,Ffor his money and personal items.
