OL,3,CArrest in connection with kidnap of
OL,4,Cman, 87, who was dumped 15 miles away
OL,6,FHe was attacked and eventually pushed
OL,7,Fout of the car on a dark road in the
OL,8,FRishworth area of West Yorkshire,
OL,9,Fofficers said.
OL,11,FThe man eventually found help by
OL,12,Fknocking on a door at around 10.40pm.
OL,14,FA 24-year-old man was arrested on
OL,15,FSunday morning in Royton, Oldham, on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of kidnap and remains in
OL,17,Fcustody for questioning, police said.
