OL,3,CArrest in connection with kidnap of
OL,4,Cman, 87, who was dumped 15 miles away
OL,6,FIt follows the arrest of a 39-year-old
OL,7,Fman on Thursday on suspicion of kidnap
OL,8,Fwho has since been released on bail
OL,9,Fpending further investigation.
OL,11,FPolice said they believed it was an
OL,12,F"isolated incident with no wider
OL,13,Fthreat to the public".
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Emma Hulston, from
OL,16,FGMP's major incident team, said
OL,17,Finvestigators were "making good
OL,18,Fprogress" on the "shocking incident".
