OL,3,CArrest in connection with kidnap of
OL,4,Cman, 87, who was dumped 15 miles away
OL,6,FShe added: "Whilst incidents of this
OL,7,Fnature can cause alarm in the
OL,8,Fcommunity, we do believe it was an
OL,9,Fisolated incident with no wider threat
OL,10,Fto the public.
OL,12,F"Specialist officers are continuing to
OL,13,Fsupport the victim and detectives are
OL,14,Fworking around the clock determined to
OL,15,Fbring offenders to justice.
OL,17,F"We are continuing to appeal to the
OL,18,Fpublic for information, dashcam or
OL,19,Fdoorbell footage that could help us
OL,20,Fsolve this crime and help hold all
OL,21,Fthose responsible accountable.
